<h2>New &amp; Noteworthy</h2>

<h5>Easter Holiday Hours</h5>All branches of the Essex County Library will be closed on Friday, March 25, Saturday, March 26, Sunday, March 27 and Monday, March 28 for the Easter Holiday.  We wish you all a Happy Easter! <br /><br />

<h5>Library users, we want to hear from you!</h5>Please take this short online survey regarding your preferred time to visit your local library branch.<a href="http://fluidsurveys.com/surveys/ecl/hours/" target="new">Click here to get started</a> <br /><br />


<h5>Rosetta Stone Language Learning Now Available!</h5> Rosetta Stone Language Learning is now available at ECL. Start learning a new language today.  <a href="http://dbproxy.essexcountylibrary.ca/login?url=http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,cpid&custid=s6935234&profile=rosetstone" target="new">Set up your free account and find out what languages we offer</a> <br /><br />

<h5>2015 Annual Report Now Available</h5>The 2015 Annual Report is now available <a href="http://esse2.ent.sirsidynix.net/custom/web/content/pdfdocs/2015_annualreport_FE2.pdf" target="new">here</a> for your viewing pleasure. Check it out to learn more about how we connect with our communities. Please contact us for an accessible document.<br /><br /> 


