<h5>ECL Staff Recommends...</h5>Winter is a great time to settle in with a good book. Our staff have some great suggestions to capture your imagination, and send you off on some fabulous adventures. <a href="http://www.essexcountylibrary.ca/client/home/search/results?qu=%22STAFFREC%22&amp;te=">See our recommendations </a><br /><br />


